id: mbedtls_tls_server
package: platform
label: TLS Server
description: >-
  This component provides support for using TLS (as a server) in Mbed TLS.
category: Platform|Security|Mbed TLS|Upper Layer
quality: production
provides:
  - name: mbedtls_tls_server
requires:
  - name: mbedtls_tls
template_contribution:
  - name: mbedtls_config
    value: MBEDTLS_SSL_SRV_C
metadata:
  sbom:
    license: Apache-2.0
    upstream:
      name: Mbed TLS
      version: v3.6.2
      supplier: Trusted Firmware
      url: https://github.com/Mbed-TLS/mbedtls.git
      comment: Mbed TLS is a C library implementing the PSA Cryptography API, cryptographic primitives, X.509 certificate manipulation and the SSL/TLS and DTLS protocols
